◆ call_inv_kin_calc_service()

bool ArmUs::call_inv_kin_calc_service ( Vector3f &  velocities,
int &  singularMatrix 
)
private

Call inverse kinematic calculation service to calculate velocities of first 3 motors to move in cartesian mode.

Parameters
velocitiesMotor velocities calculated by service, returns [0, 0, 0] if service call failed or singular matrix detected
singularMatrix1 of singular matrix detected, 0 otherwise
Returns
true if call to service was successful
false if call to service was unsuccessful
